data.description:
Welcome to this 2,403 square feet well kept three-bedroom, two-bathroom home in Pearl, MS! The entryway opens into a spacious living area, providing ample room for comfort and relaxation.

The kitchen includes a cozy keeping room with a fireplace, perfect for those cozy evenings. Additionally, the living room boasts another fireplace, making this home warm and inviting.

Enjoy meals in the dining room, find focus in the office/desk area, and relax in the recently enclosed patio—a versatile space for various needs.

Enclosed patio to enjoy the days and nights. Sprinkler system installed for landscaping.

Conveniently located near the interstate and shopping, this home offers both comfort and accessibility in a desirable location.
